# Yoyo migrations live here.
#
# Filename convention: NNNN_description.sql (sequential, matters for order).
# The platform's db helper applies pending migrations on Lambda cold start;
# locally they apply on backend container startup.
#
# Example:
#   0001_initial.sql
#   0002_notes_table.sql
#
# Each file is plain SQL. For destructive (DROP) migrations, document why.
# Yoyo also supports rollback markers if you need them; see yoyo docs.
